				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainKeSeluruhTubuh" } Nyeri menjalar ke seluruh tubuh lain
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainPerut.Single{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplain", :value => "Perut" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainPerut" } Perut
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainLengan.Single{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplain", :value => "Lengan" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainLengan" } Lengan
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainDada.Single{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplain", :value => "Dada" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainDada" } Dada
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainOther.Single{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplain", :value => "other" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainOther" } Lainnya

			%br
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestPainComplainOther.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%hr

			%label.medium.Single.Item 7. Jelaskan nama obat dan lama pemakainnya sehubungan dengan gangguan pencernaan :
			%br    
			%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestDrugsName.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr

			%div.RadioButton.PositionerLeft
				%label.medium.Single.Item 8. Apakah obat tersebut diperoleh berdasarkan resep dokter?
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipeNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipe", :value => "false" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipeNo" } Tidak
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipeYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipe", :value => "true" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestDoctorRecipeYes" } Ya
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Nama Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestDoctorName.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Alamat Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestDoctorAddress.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr

			%label.medium.Single.Item 9. Mohon jelaskan secara rinci pada kolom di bawah ini jenis dan hasil pemeriksaan kesehatan yang dilakukan sehubungan dengan gangguan pencernaan ini, termasuk tanggal pemeriksaannya. (Lampirkan fotokopi hasil pemeriksaan)
			%br    
			%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestResultOfTheExamination.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr

			%label.medium.Single.Item 10. Apakah pernah mendapatkan perawatan rumah sakit sehubungan dengan gangguan pencernaan tersebut?
			%br
			%div.RadioButton.PositionerLeft
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCare", :value => "false" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareNo" } Tidak
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCare", :value => "true" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareYes" } Ya

			%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareWhen.Medium.Single.PositionerRight.Margin{ :type => "text", "data-field" => "date" }
			%label#LabelPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareWhen.Wrap.Single.PositionerRight.Margin Kapan
			%br

			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Lama Perawatan
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareHowLong.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Nama Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareDoctorName.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Alamat Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestHospitalCareDoctorAddress.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr

			%div.RadioButton.PositionerLeft
				%label.medium.Single.Item 11. Apakah sampai saat ini masih dalam pengobatan?
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatmentNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatment", :value => "false" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatmentNo" } Tidak
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatmentYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatment", :value => "true" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestInTreatmentYes" } Ya
			%br

			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Alasan
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestTreatmentReason.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Nama Obat
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestTreatmentDrugsName.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Nama Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestTreatmentDoctorName.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%div.ContainerFit 
				%label.Long.Single.PositionerLeft Alamat Dokter
				%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestTreatmentDoctorAddress.Full.Single.Item.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr
			%div.RadioButton.PositionerLeft
				%label.medium.Single.Item 12. Dalam 2 tahun terakhir ini, apakah Anda pernah tidak masuk kerja karena gangguan ini ?
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYear", :value => "false" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearNo" } Tidak
				%div.Separator
				%input#RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYear", :value => "true" }
				%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearYes" } Ya	
			%br
			%label#LabelPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearWhen.Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft.Margin Kapan
			%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearWhen.Medium.Single.PositionerLeft.Margin{ :type => "text", "data-field" => "date" }	
			%label#LabelPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearHowLong.Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft.Margin dan berapa lama?
			%input#TextPolicyHolderDigestNoOfficeEntryInYearHowLong.Medium.Single.PositionerLeft.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%br
			%hr

			%label.medium.Single.Item 13. Mohon sebutkan bila ada informasi lain sehubungan dengan kondisi kesehatan anda yang mungkin dapat membantu proses pengajuan Asuransi ini  
			%input#AreaPolicyHolderDigestOtherHealthCondition.Full.Multi.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
			%br
			%hr

